summary: can u do mpreg reader into carol x reader where the reader where the reader is in the tower stark together with the avengers and...
question: can u do mpreg reader into carol x reader where the reader where the reader is in the tower stark together with the avengers and everyone takes care of her
answer:
• “got him!”
  • “carol, you gotta let me finish it before you just —”
  • “there is no time! I want this thing as far away as possible from you!”
  • was it an atomic bomb coming right at you? an extraterrestrial being that came to invade the earth? perhaps an evil robot trying to terminate human life?
  • nope
  • it was a cockroach you were trying to kill
  • and carol has just completely roasted it
  • you were only 3 months into your pregnancy but everyone around you acted as if you were a delicate china doll
  • and carol, above everyone else, has somehow managed to outdone THAT
  • she wasn’t usually the worried type but she has been panicky around you lately
  • too panicky
  • don’t get me wrong, it’s not like you were going on missions anyway
  • you stopped that 3 months ago
  • but stepping on a ladder to reach the top shelf? why do that when carol could just fly?
  • (yes, she flied for that because she was that extra)
  • bending down to tie your shoe? carol was already there to tie it for you
  • god forbid, what if you had to go and pick up your own food from the store around the corner?
  • what? an outrageous idea! out of this world! carol would just pick it up for you!
  • to be completely honest, it sometimes drove you insane
  • you weren’t left alone for more than two minutes and it was only your first trimester
  • two more of that? you had no idea how you were going to cope
  • but you still wouldn’t have it any other way
  • you loved how she took care of you
  • how she cared about the baby as much as you do if not even more
  • but most importantly
  • you loved how you got to spend more time with your girlfriend
  • how she was always around
  • how your days would always start with her putting tiny little kisses all over your belly
  • how she would then mumble “good morning” and “hey there”s to both you and the baby
  • how she would do the same thing over again just to say “good night”
  • and most importantly
  • how she was always there 
  • and always will be there for you and the baby
